[SPEAKER_04] trebalo bi to znanje,

674
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:15,519
[SPEAKER_04] ovaj, evo, vidjeti,

675
00:42:15,519 --> 00:42:18,800
[SPEAKER_04] mi smo otvorili različite teme,

676
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:21,320
[SPEAKER_04] jedva čekam, evo, ljetnu školu,

677
00:42:21,320 --> 00:42:23,380
[SPEAKER_04] dragi slušatelji, dragi gledatelji,

678
00:42:23,380 --> 00:42:25,940
[SPEAKER_04] ja vas isto srdečno pozivam,

679
00:42:25,940 --> 00:42:27,599
[SPEAKER_04] prijavite se,

680
00:42:27,599 --> 00:42:28,960
[SPEAKER_04] do kad su prijave?

681
00:42:29,699 --> 00:42:31,840
[SPEAKER_03] Do prvoga sedmoga,

682
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:34,219
[SPEAKER_03] ali do 31. sedmoga je još moguće,

683
00:42:34,219 --> 00:42:36,019
[SPEAKER_03] moguće se javiti,

684
00:42:36,019 --> 00:42:36,659
[SPEAKER_03] ostvariti,

685
00:42:36,659 --> 00:42:39,199
[SPEAKER_03] oni koji ne sudjeluje preko razmusa,

686
00:42:39,199 --> 00:42:41,400
[SPEAKER_03] moraju platiti određeni iznos,

687
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,760
[SPEAKER_03] koji pokriva minimalno,

688
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:45,179
[SPEAKER_03] dakle, zaista su minimalni troški.

689
00:42:45,179 --> 00:42:47,300
[SPEAKER_04] To je smještaj predpostavljanih hrana.

690
00:42:47,300 --> 00:42:49,460
[SPEAKER_03] I svi popretni, dakle,

691
00:42:49,460 --> 00:42:50,500
[SPEAKER_03] sadržaj kao što imamo,

692
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:52,099
[SPEAKER_03] imamo jedan izlet,

693
00:42:52,099 --> 00:42:54,280
[SPEAKER_03] dakle, sve je to onda uključeno u cijenu.

694
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:57,659
[SPEAKER_04] A lokacija će biti kao i prošle dvije godine,

695
00:42:57,900 --> 00:43:00,679
[SPEAKER_04] na fakultetu u svojučilištu u Splijču,

696
00:43:00,679 --> 00:43:01,199
[SPEAKER_04] je li tako?

697
00:43:01,199 --> 00:43:01,780
[SPEAKER_04] Tako je.

698
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:02,460
[SPEAKER_04] Evo,

699
00:43:02,460 --> 00:43:04,179
[SPEAKER_04] draga Marijana,

700
00:43:04,179 --> 00:43:07,900
[SPEAKER_04] hvala ti što si bila još jednom naša gošća,

701
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,639
[SPEAKER_04] želimo puno uspjeha,

702
00:43:09,639 --> 00:43:11,940
[SPEAKER_04] Božjeg blagoslova,

703
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:12,440
[SPEAKER_04] evo,

704
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:13,639
[SPEAKER_04] neka gospodin vodi,

705
00:43:13,639 --> 00:43:17,280
[SPEAKER_04] neka on ovakve velike projekte vodi,

706
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:21,820
[SPEAKER_04] neka duh sveti nas blagoslovi za ovakve stvari,

707
00:43:21,940 --> 00:43:22,659
[SPEAKER_04] neka on vodi,

708
00:43:22,659 --> 00:43:28,039
[SPEAKER_04] a neka mi budemo instrument preko kojih onda on može raditi.

709
00:43:28,039 --> 00:43:31,099
[SPEAKER_04] Dragi slušatelji, dragi gledatelji,

710
00:43:31,099 --> 00:43:36,719
[SPEAKER_04] evo, hvala vam još jedan put što ste pratili emisiju Franjina ekonomija.

711
00:43:36,719 --> 00:43:39,760
[SPEAKER_04] Moje ime je Katarina Bukša,

712
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:43,039
[SPEAKER_04] ja sam urednica i voditeljica emisije,

713
00:43:43,039 --> 00:43:46,760
[SPEAKER_04] a tehnički urednik je danas bio Ivan Zaradić.

714
00:43:47,599 --> 00:43:48,679
[SPEAKER_04] Hvala nisu si, Marija.

